  m_text: "<align=center><size=120%><color=#D2691E>GETTING STARTED</color></size></align>\n<align=left><b><color=#8B4513>\U0001FA93
    How to Harvest:</color></b>\nEquip your <b>Axe</b> and strike the trunk! You
    will notice the tree <b>shake</b> with every successful hit. Keep swinging until
    the tree falls to claim your <color=#8B4513>Oak</color>!\n\n<b><color=#C04000>\U0001F341
    Looking for Maple?</color></b>\nHigher-quality <b>Maple Trees</b> can be found
    deeper in the forest. However, that path is currently <b><color=red>LOCKED</color></b>.\n\n<b><color=#32CD32>Goal:</color></b>
    Collect <b>5,000 Oak</b> to clear the path and unlock the Maple Forest!</align>"
